**Note.** Especially, if neither of $\alpha$ and $\beta$ is right angle,
the formula of the theorem may be written
$$\frac{a}{\cos\alpha}+\frac{b}{\cos\beta} = \frac{c}{\cos\alpha\,\cos\beta}.$$
